question_id: Kota mana yang memiliki jumlah pelanggan terbanyak? Sertakan nama kota dan jumlah pelanggannya.
sql_query:
SELECT
  c.city,
  COUNT(c.customer_id) AS jumlah_pelanggan
FROM customer AS c
JOIN address AS ca
  ON c.address_id = ca.address_id
JOIN city AS ci
  ON ca.city_id = ci.city_id
GROUP BY
  c.city
ORDER BY
  jumlah_pelanggan DESC
